Change Log

v 0.0.4
===============================================================================
Removed dependency on boost.

v 0.0.3
===============================================================================
Added getopt and daemonize support. Added sysV style init script so daemon
can be run as service. Should now be ready to replace ovirt-identify-node in
ovirt-node.

v 0.0.2
===============================================================================
Now tracks hypervisor type and arch using libvirt.


v 0.0.1
===============================================================================
Initial version using autotools.

Tracks Node, CPU and NIC info. Provides method to physically identify NIC.

